{"tid":1647012,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"有無講故巴絲可以用近日疑團做題材寫小說","createTime":"2019-10-11T14:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T14:33:43.000Z","uid":37053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"33bfcb5d106a48be7287ce72a1e238d77373ae01","tid":1647012,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:30:52.000Z","msg":"淨係831有無死人 <br />\n入面發生咗咩事已經好引人入勝<br />\n<br />\n唔係想消費死者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過事實係一篇好的小說最能夠令人keep住討論 <br />\n甚至令更多人去搜羅同編輯真相<br />\n<br />\n好似西營盤站鬼故 <br />\n連我阿媽都問我個站係咪真係有嗰層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅Van故甚至可以拍成電影繼續討論<br />\n<br />\n如果有個小說寫全裸浮屍案<br />\n用受害者角度寫下案情<br />\n甚至以靈媒身份寫<br />\n相信都會幾好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86edf9bfda5e28212424a6487811842c1191ed20","tid":1647012,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:31:37.000Z","msg":"831 打死人"},{"pid":"398dfb13bb5f9e658fbcfe58f54ac4d7bf5f3f02","tid":1647012,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"721 唔見人"},{"pid":"1c8a12c5c4a3a2632cb49638c616e637e1b62f47","tid":1647012,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:32:02.000Z","msg":"10月1 槍殺人"},{"pid":"a5daaf05abbd61ed95a930fd71ec51cb7cb54a1a","tid":1647012,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:32:15.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"275e9972ee48f9011de74e752efcb6fbe00d20c3","tid":1647012,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:32:27.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"1984f3c4904f8885d33b8454610317e0ad7c4079","tid":1647012,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:32:42.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"283d13145ce30351373b847bdd09254bb806949e","tid":1647012,"uid":37053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re